---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Wie_Team from '../assets/images/wie-team.jpg'

import Instagram from '../assets/instagram.svg';
import LinkedIn from '../assets/linkedin.svg';
---

<Layout>
	<section class="relative bg-[url('../assets/images/hero-wie-2025.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat min-h-[95vh] flex items-center justify-center text-white">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>

		<div class="relative flex flex-col gap-6 text-center text-off-white px-6">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl uppercase tracking-wide">
				leading the future together
			</h1>
			<h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold relative uppercase">
				17th annual ieee wie wine and cheese
			</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-col gap-3">
			<img src={Instagram.src} width="30" height="30" alt="" class="z-100 filter invert brightness-0"/>
			<img src={LinkedIn.src} width="30" height="30" alt="" class="z-100 filter invert brightness-0"/>
			<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">   <path d="..." /> </svg>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-off-white py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<div class="float-right w-72 md:w-9/20 ml-4 mb-3 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl ring-1 ring-black/10">
				<div class="aspect-4/3 md:aspect-16/10">
					<img
						src={Wie_Team.src}
						alt="IEEE WIE team"
						class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
						loading="lazy"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-6 mb-3">
				<p class="text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500">
					leading the future together
				</p>
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading-fam font-bold text-off-black tracking-tight">
					Hello and Welcome!
				</h2>
				</div>
			<div class="text-xl space-y-6">
				<p class="leading-relaxed">
					Locally, the IEEE WIE student branches at the University of Ottawa and Carleton University seek this brighter future by connecting students with industry leaders, like yourself, through events such as the annual Wine & Cheese. We have put together this event for sixteen years now, to benefit you in seeking the best candidates for internships, coops, and future coworkers.
				</p>
				<p class="leading-relaxed">
					Just like you, we think that the future looks brighter when everyone is working together and contributing to build and innovate. This is why IEEE Women in Engineering (WIE) is the largest international professional organization dedicated to promoting women engineers and scientists. Our mission is to facilitate the global recruitment and retention of women in technical disciplines through affirmative action. IEEE WIE envisions a vibrant community of IEEE women, men and people from all over the gender spectrum collectively using their diverse talents and perspectives to accelerate progress toward a sustainable future with innovative technology.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>